<strong> Question</strong>
find fx, fy, fxx, fyy, fxy and fyx.

$f(x,y)=x/y$

<strong>Answer</strong>

$f(x,y)=x/y$

$f_x=1/y$

$f_y=-x/y^2$

$f_{xx} = 0$

$f_{yy} = -2x/y^3$

$f_{xy} = -1/y^2$

$f_{yx} = -1/y^2$
